This paper deals with the problem of navigation in complex environments, which is a common topic in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of reinforcement learning and auxiliary tasks also suggests a focus on learning-based approaches, which is relevant to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
